		<main id="main" class="site-main" role="main"><article id="post-211" class="post-211 page type-page status-publish hentry"><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title">School Closures</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">
		<h3>School Closure Information</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight:400;">In the event of school closings due to inclement weather, MNCS will send out an alert via the Honeywell Instant Alert system. If your personal information has changed, please take the time to add/edit your contact information using the </span><a href="http://www.newcountryschool.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Honeywell-Parent-User-Interface1.pdf"><span style="font-weight:400;">Honeywell Parent User Interface</span></a><span style="font-weight:400;">. Please click on the link below to download instructions for setting up a Honeywell account.</span></p>
<p>Contact Anthony Sonnek with any questions/concerns:  asonnek@newcountryschool.com</p>
<p><span style="font-weight:400;">Weather Updates: All weather-related school closings and delays will be announced on the following:</span></p>
<p><i><span style="font-weight:400;">Television Channels</span></i><span style="font-weight:400;"> – CBS 3, WCCO 4, ABC\KSTP 5&amp;6, FOX\KMSP 9, KARE 11, and KEYC 12</span></p>
<p><i><span style="font-weight:400;">Radio Stations</span></i><span style="font-weight:400;"> – WCCO, KEEZ, KMKO, KRBI, and KYSM</span></p>
<p><a title="honeywell-parent-user-interface1" href="https://newcountryschool.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/honeywell-parent-user-interface1.pdf">honeywell-parent-user-interface1</a> (pdf)</p>
